OL,7,FA man who threw a six-year-old boy off
OL,8,Fthe Tate Modern has been found guilty
OL,9,Fof attacking two nurses at Broadmoor
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FJonty Bravery kicked a female nurse in
OL,13,Fthe thigh and "clawed" at the face of
OL,14,Fanother, leaving her with blood
OL,15,Fdripping down her cheek.
OL,17,FThe 24-year-old was handed a life
OL,18,Fsentence for hurling a French boy from
OL,19,FTate Modern's 10th-storey balcony in
OL,20,F2019.
