OL,7,FThe boy survived the 100ft (30m) fall,
OL,8,Fbut suffered life-changing injuries,
OL,9,Fincluding a bleed on the brain and
OL,10,Fmultiple broken bones.
OL,12,FBravery, who is autistic is now being
OL,13,Fheld at Broadmoor, a high-security
OL,14,Fpsychiatric hospital in Crowthorne,
OL,15,FBerkshire.
OL,17,FHe chose not to attend his trial at
OL,18,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,19,FThursday, where he was found guilty of
OL,20,Fassaulting nurses Linda McKinlay and
OL,21,FKate Mastalerz in September 2024.
