OL,7,FProsecutor Tom Heslop said Bravery has
OL,8,Fto be monitored by three members of
OL,9,Fstaff "24 hours a day, seven days a
OL,10,Fweek", and is kept in a room with only
OL,11,Fa mattress in it.
OL,13,F"At around 9.30 at night, Mr Bravery
OL,14,Fasked to go to the toilet," he said.
OL,16,F"After he used the bathroom, he
OL,17,Fattempted to climb a ledge and throw
OL,18,Fhimself from it."
