OL,7,FThe nurses tried to restrain him,
OL,8,Fputting him on his mattress before
OL,9,Fturning him onto his back, Mr Heslop
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FBravery "kicked out towards Ms
OL,13,FMastalerz", hitting her in the thigh,
OL,14,Fthe court heard.
OL,16,FHe also "clawed across" Ms McKinlay's
OL,17,Fface, leaving her with blood dripping
OL,18,Fdown her cheek, the prosecutor said.
