OL,7,FBody-worn footage played to the court
OL,8,Fshowed the nurses struggling on the
OL,9,Ffloor with Bravery before other staff
OL,10,Frush into the room to help.
OL,12,FA panicked staff member can be heard
OL,13,Fshouting "Jesus Christ do something".
OL,15,FMs McKinlay told the court it was the
OL,16,Ffirst time she had been attacked at
OL,17,FBroadmoor in her long career.
OL,19,F"Jonty climbed up trying to get on to
OL,20,Fthe windowsill," she said.
